# .lfs-allowed-paths
#
# Glob-patterns for paths exempted from the 1 MB binary-size limit
# enforced by scripts/hooks/check-large-binaries.mjs.
#
# Format:
#   - One pattern per line.
#   - `*` matches anything except `/`.
#   - `**` matches across `/`.
#   - `#` comments and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Add an entry only when the binary is genuinely required to ship in the
# repo (not via LFS or CDN). Document the reason inline so reviewers
# don't have to guess.
#
# Examples (commented out — add only when actually needed):
# packages/game-client/public/audio/master-loop.mp3   # legacy gameplay loop, replaced post-pilot
# legacy/unity-client/Assets/Sprites/big-bg.png       # already-tracked legacy asset
